{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a681711d51","title":"转发苏南区党委关于召开民主党派座谈会的报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e23b182fad","index":0,"year":1951,"month":1,"day":25,"articleId":"a681711d51"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji30","name":"毛泽东全集第30卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/30-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji30":{"comments":[{"id":"84a621c930","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"a681711d51","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"罗迈，即李维汉，当时任中共中央统战部部长。"},{"id":"5ed11da2e9","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"a681711d51","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指中共苏南区委员会统战部1950年12月26日关于苏南区第一次民主党派座谈会的情况给华东局并华东局统战部的报告。苏南区党委统战部召开的这次民主党派座谈会，就中国共产党同民主党派的关系和民主党派的工作交流了情况，统一了思想，加强了相互间的团结，到会各党派代表都非常满意。"}],"contents":[{"id":"3c75652ea8","type":"title","text":"转发苏南区党委关于召开民主党派座谈会的报告的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"a681711d51"},{"id":"84a621c930","type":"paragraph","text":"罗运同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"a681711d51"},{"id":"5ed11da2e9","type":"paragraph","text":"此件可印发到统战会议的各同志，并可要他们带回去给更多的同志看看。请要各中央局，分局，省市区党委的统战部一律定期召集，或有大事召集各民主党派代表人士开会，如苏南这次会议一样，并向中央统战部作报告，不开会不报告者认为失职","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"a681711d51"},{"id":"9654af5dc7","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"a681711d51"},{"id":"eb031571d1","type":"paragraph","text":"一月廿五日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"a681711d51"}],"page":{"id":"5184d0398c","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"a681711d51","start":74,"end":74}}}},"__N_SSG":true}